---
// What We Do Section - Combined Story
// Start with the right question → Layered methodology diagram → How we do it
---

<section class="what-we-do section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="big-bold-text">START WITH THE RIGHT QUESTION.</h2>

    <p class="intro-text">
      We don't just build what you ask for. We discover what your business actually needs. Every product is different. Every business has unique patterns. We don't rush discovery—we do it right.
    </p>

    <!-- Methodology Diagram -->
    <div class="methodology-diagram">
      <h3 class="diagram-title">Our Methodology</h3>
      <p class="diagram-subtitle">We build everything from your user requirement down. Underneath the product surface lies a solid foundation, built through testing and iteration.</p>

      <div class="layers-stack">
        <div class="layer product-surface-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">Product Surface</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer overlay-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">Control & Safety</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer tech-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">Technology & Tools</span>
          <span class="layer-source">from Operation & System</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer user-req-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">User Requirement</span>
          <span class="layer-source">from Goal & Expectations</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer goal-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">Goal & Expectations</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer foundation-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">Foundation</span>
          <div class="foundation-pills">
            <span>Problem Statement</span>
            <span>Workflow Design</span>
            <span>Data Foundations</span>
          </div>
          <span class="foundation-note">Built through test and tries</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer governance-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">Governance | Maintenance | Improvement</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer data-pillars-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">Real-time Data Pillars</span>
          <div class="data-pills">
            <span>Data Management</span>
            <span>Data Quality</span>
            <span>Privacy & Compliance</span>
            <span>Data Stewardship</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="methodology-note">
        Every product is built on validated foundations, not assumptions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three Steps - After Diagram -->
    <div class="how-we-do-it">
      <h3 class="section-subtitle">How We Do It:</h3>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">1</span>
          <h4 class="step-title">Foundation Discovery</h4>
          <p class="step-description">
            We dig into your business patterns to refine your problem statement. Together, we define your product's goals and expectations—the foundation everything else is built on.
          </p>
          <p class="step-deliverable">
            <strong>What you get:</strong> Clear problem definition, validated business goals, project expectations documented
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">2</span>
          <h4 class="step-title">Proof of Concept & Research</h4>
          <p class="step-description">
            We plan and conduct research with your real end-users. Through structured interviews and testing, we validate assumptions and uncover requirements you didn't know you had.
          </p>
          <p class="step-deliverable">
            <strong>What you get:</strong> User insights from actual interviews, validated requirements, research documentation
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">3</span>
          <h4 class="step-title">Deliverables</h4>
          <p class="step-description">
            You receive your first prototype sketch and a comprehensive Business Requirements Specification (BRS)—complete with KPIs. This becomes your roadmap for development.
          </p>
          <p class="step-deliverable">
            <strong>What you get:</strong> Initial prototype, firm BRS with documented KPIs, development-ready specifications
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="ai-note">
      <strong>Note on AI:</strong> We use Generative AI to draft documents and prototypes—but never for thinking. Every insight, every decision, every strategy comes from human analysis of your unique business.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .what-we-do {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .what-we-do .big-bold-text {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* Methodology Diagram */
  .methodology-diagram {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: var(--space-4xl) auto;
  }

  .diagram-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .diagram-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .layers-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .layer {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    min-height: 48px;
    position: relative;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .layer:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  /* Product Surface Layer (Top) */
  .product-surface-layer {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-xl);
    min-height: 60px;
  }

  .product-surface-layer .layer-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* Overlay Layer */
  .overlay-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-warm);
  }

  /* Tech Layer */
  .tech-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  /* User Requirement Layer */
  .user-req-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  /* Goal Layer */
  .goal-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  /* Foundation Layer */
  .foundation-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    background: rgba(208, 120, 85, 0.1);
  }

  .foundation-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .foundation-pills span {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: var(--color-accent-warm);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .foundation-note {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  /* Governance Layer */
  .governance-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  /* Data Pillars Layer */
  .data-pillars-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    background: rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.1);
  }

  .layer-label {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .layer-source {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .data-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .data-pills span {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .methodology-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  /* How We Do It Section */
  .how-we-do-it {
    margin-top: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .step {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .step:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background-color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .step-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .step-deliverable {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    padding: var(--space-md) 0 var(--space-md) var(--space-md);
    background-color: transparent;
    border-radius: 0;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  .step-deliverable strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .ai-note {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: var(--space-4xl) auto 0;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-note strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .layers-stack {
      gap: var(--space-xs);
    }

    .layer {
      padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
      min-height: 44px;
    }

    .product-surface-layer {
      padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
      min-height: 52px;
    }

    .product-surface-layer .layer-label {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }

    .layer-label {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }

    .foundation-pills,
    .data-pills {
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .foundation-pills span,
    .data-pills span {
      font-size: 10px;
      padding: 3px 10px;
    }

    .steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .step {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
